segments.source_content:
---
id: community
title: Join our Community
---
Ent maintainers, contributors and users hang out in our Discord server and the #ent channel in the Gophers Slack workspace.

translations.zh-CN: Ent 的维护者、贡献者和用户活跃于我们的 Discord 服务器以及 Gophers Slack 工作区的 #ent 频道。

segments.source_content: To Join our Discord server, click [here](https://discord.gg/qZmPgTE6RX).

translations.zh-CN: 点击[此处](https://discord.gg/qZmPgTE6RX)加入我们的 Discord 服务器。

segments.source_content: To join the discussion in slack:

translations.zh-CN: 加入 Slack 讨论的步骤：

segments.source_content:
1. Sign up to the Gophers Slack workspace via the [invite link](https://invite.slack.golangbridge.org/).
2. Join the #ent channel manually or via [this link](https://app.slack.com/client/T029RQSE6/C01FMSQDT53). (it will work only if you are logged in to slack from your browser)

translations.zh-CN:
1. 通过[邀请链接](https://invite.slack.golangbridge.org/)注册 Gophers Slack 工作区。
2. 手动加入 #ent 频道，或通过[此链接](https://app.slack.com/client/T029RQSE6/C01FMSQDT53)加入（仅当您已通过浏览器登录 Slack 时有效）。
